data.description: OFFERING $10,000 SELLER CREDIT towards Buyer's Closing Cost or Rate Buy Down. Featuring 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms. The kitchen features SS appliances, white cabinets, pendent lighting, and Quartz countertops, large island, pantry and office nook. Built in bar and Greatroom. The owner's suite has access to the patio and features a luxurious bathroom with a soaking tub, tiled shower, and dual vanities. The backyard faces North with views of the mountains and features an oversized covered patio with pavers and power shade, built-in gas fireplace, AquaScience Misting/Fogging system to keep you cool in the summers.  The yard is complete with synthetic turf , citrus trees and a raised bed for flowers or garden. Front LED Trim lights. 3-car tandem garage, RV Parking, and Tuff Shed.
